									<h5 id="subject_173491">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/index.php?topic=10744.msg173491#msg173491" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jun 2017] - Gangsters and Crime Lords - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #7 on:</strong> June 27, 2017, 06:36:53 AM &#187;</div>
