									<h5 id="subject_173660">
										<a href="http://fantasy-faction.com/forum/index.php?topic=10744.msg173660#msg173660" rel="nofollow">Re: [Jun 2017] - Gangsters and Crime Lords - Submission Thread</a>
									</h5>
									<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>Reply #12 on:</strong> July 01, 2017, 01:50:31 PM &#187;</div>
									<div id="msg_173660_quick_mod"></div>
								</div>
