							<div class="signature" id="msg_173660_signature">&quot;She will need coffee soon, or molecular degeneration will set in. Her French phrasing will take over even more strongly, and soon she will dissolve into a puddle of alienation and Kierkegaardian despair.&quot;&nbsp; ~ Jmack<br /><br />Wishy washy lyricism&nbsp;and maudlin unrequited love are my specialty - so said Lady_Ty</div>
